For a list of Gentoo update servers, run this and choose a few servers:

mirrorselect -i -o >> /etc/portage/make.conf

For the Gentoo rsync server, run this and choose one server:

mirrorselect -i -r -o

Copy that server to the

/etc/portage/repos.conf/gentoo.conf

file, setting the variable sync-uri to it. For example:

sync-uri = rsync://rsync.uk.gentoo.org/gentoo-portage
*



emerge --sync

per ottenere l'intero albero di portage
emerge-webrsync
